Zero MMIX
---------
- implement Knuth's MMIX architecture in software (virtual machine)
- utilise the zas assembler and/or implement one for MMIX-syntax
- experiment with graphical development tools
  - tag functions/lines with breakpoints and profiler events (start, stop)
  - allow signal breakpoints
  - stack-based RPN calculator frontend
    - refactor zpc
  - debugger
    - stack
      - caller and callee frames
      - resolve addresses to symbols
      - backtrace/unwind
      - register/variable contents (hex, dec, oct, bin display modes)
  - profiler
    - measure execution times in microseconds (gettimeofday()) and clock cycles

